ts/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地應該想香港死添啦"},{"pid":"4de9c45c27fc3e8177c6aa922acdbffdfcec2c97","tid":1200201,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"樓主拎白卡"},{"pid":"4f371f5ec05b9f86933f5bd7d9052917afce96a0","tid":1200201,"uid":5151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"做假新聞同共產黨有乜分別"},{"pid":"b1a73f6691c32ecbc198ccf7ee3331acd58705c7","tid":1200201,"uid":241310,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NifzLR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNifzLR3.jpg&h=5e78dfc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話晒你幾秒鐘，入去留個言，可以嘅話叫多啲朋友來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n〔置頂〕唔通溫和派就無嘢可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1199622/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1199622/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟通知咗大家我聽日會去同朋友拎錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果順路可以join埋，<strong>中環所有銀行</strong>都有總行，你拎港紙／美金都無所謂，甚至問開戶詳情都得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最鍾意<strong>多人喺中環</strong>來睇我拎錢，你唔撳都可以來睇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好問有無用</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：非鍵戰，就算聽日得我同朋友同記者都照去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n我哩個係新自發嘅行動，想畀更多人知道<br />\n哩個活動十分低成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係需要你排一排隊，去撳錢；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果多人，甚至可能撳唔到錢</span></strong><br />\n適合有包袱，又想做嘢嘅人<br />\n<br />\n大家要知道散播虛假消息係犯法，唔好為咗更多人來睇「我」撳錢，就去作料！<br />\n已經搵咗記者朋友，歡迎大家繼續share出去！<br />\n同時唔好煽動其他人！其他人陣間見到都去撳錢就&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n可能有人唔認同，覺得我做嘅杯水車薪，但唔做過又點知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f333c449422e354f76669c2ced242f6a16b1b215","tid":1200201,"uid":225734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5e016211d6bc94d0b87a85e80a2f353e4964d21","tid":1200201,"uid":3914,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"根本無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話廣州 我以前外國讀書識嘅一個深圳frd對香港時事都有理解都完全唔知尋日咩事<br />\n上面封鎖晒消息架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"我上面表弟知好多人遊行，但唔知乜嘢事。仲話新聞cut剩5分鐘。"},{"pid":"df5e9326bf7ed0e8b6c1e977c6820de2dd676206","tid":1200201,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f333c449422e354f76669c2ced242f6a16b1b215","tid":1200201,"uid":225734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5e016211d6bc94d0b87a85e80a2f353e4964d21","tid":1200201,"uid":3914,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"根本無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話廣州 我以前外國讀書識嘅一個深圳frd對香港時事都有理解都完全唔知尋日咩事<br />\n上面封鎖晒消息架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"我上面表弟知好多人遊行，但唔知乜嘢事。仲話新聞cut剩5分鐘。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"果5分鐘係咪又話遊行係撐個柒婆呀，佢地好撚興架嘛，屌佢老尾on99"},{"pid":"c99d260665ba07c0cb2086bb0af9b551cc7303d5","tid":1200201,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f333c449422e354f76669c2ced242f6a16b1b215","tid":1200201,"uid":225734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5e016211d6bc94d0b87a85e80a2f353e4964d21","tid":1200201,"uid":3914,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"根本無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話廣州 我以前外國讀書識嘅一個深圳frd對香港時事都有理解都完全唔知尋日咩事<br />\n上面封鎖晒消息架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\